Package: LSTtools
Version: 0.0.1
Type: Package
Title: Tools to analyze Land Surface Temperature
Description: Tools for the analysis of Land Surface Temperature 
 (LST) data derived from Landsat and MODIS satellites. 
 It provides a number of pre-processing, processing and 
 post-processing tools to conduct Urban Heat Island (UHI) 
 assessments.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/RichardLemoine/LSTtools
BugReports: https://github.com/RichardLemoine/LSTtools/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports: raster (>= 3.3-13), gdalUtils (>= 2.0.3.2), rgdal (>= 1.5-12),
 sp (>= 1.3-1), usdm (>= 1.1-18), spatialEco (>= 1.3-2)
Suggests: 
    MODIS,
    MODIStsp,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    RColorBrewer
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
LazyData: true
NeedsCompilation: no
